column5: i hear the weather is bad in n.w.o,are the lakes froze over yet?Maybe one of the"locals" could tell me.thanks
We have 3in. of snow, some small lakes got ice, temp. is 20 degrees3 more weeks to go.
Some shallow lakes froze over in NW Ontario....2in of ice...some of the boys talking about doing a walk out fish on a lake 100km from Thunder Bay this weekend. Be carefull out there guys.
